<title>USA: Hvide Marine in $93.3 million offering.</title>
<headline>Hvide Marine in $93.3 million offering.</headline>
<dateline>FORT LAUDERDALE, Fla. 1997-01-31</dateline>
<text>
<p>Hvide Marine Inc said on Friday it has begun a public offering of four million Class A common shares, priced at $24.875, in a bid to raise $93.3 million.</p>
<p>The funds will be used in part to complete previously announced acquisitions and reduce debt, the company said.</p>
<p>Hvide Marine is a marine support and transportation services company.</p>
